{"tid":2050599,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"原來香港自古以來就受當權者欺壓","createTime":"2020-06-04T08:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T17:33:42.000Z","uid":45270,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4b765b665555ab5f43f774bac746aa201b4df1ee","tid":2050599,"uid":45270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:34:23.000Z","msg":"香港人要建國，必先熟讀自身歷史，再推論未來。最近讀緊本梁啟智嘅 《香港第一課》，入面講到香港嘅歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呼之則來揮之則去的邊陲<br />\n<br />\n（節錄）⋯我們可問一問這片現在叫作&ldquo;香港&rdquo;的地方，自古以來是在怎樣的意義下演繹其所謂中國領土的地位；中國自古以來是如何理解這個今天稱為&ldquo;香港&rdquo;的地方；而以此構成的關系又如何建立不同時代的中國對香港的理解或誤解。<br />\n<br />\n我們不妨從蜑家人的歷史開始談這個故事。蜑家人是指華南沿岸的水上人，往往以江海為家，居無定所。中國傳統文化以土地為基礎，要到水上生活的人往往是因避亂、兵敗、被罰而遷往大海的，本來就是邊緣地帶的邊緣群體。千年以來，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> <strong>蜑家人一直過著被歧視、被流放、被徵召，然後被鎮壓的命運。</span> </strong> 蜑族人自漢代以來便被禁止在陸上建屋，不得與陸地居民通婚和出席考試，也不可以購買田土與官位。宋代的時候，朝廷曾招引蜑民為海軍，放寬私鹽。後來南宋經濟衰退，政府重新壟斷造鹽，蜑民反抗，引發了1197年的&ldquo;大嶼山屠殺&rdquo;，蜑民傷亡枕藉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對中央來說，邊陲地帶往往扮演這種呼之則來，揮之則去的角色，只因其對中央的價值而存在，當地人本身的生活是無須關心的。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 買咗正版書，支持知識產權 <br />\n呢本書本身係中大教授梁啟智寫 點樣帶中国學生理解香港局勢"},{"pid":"92dfb7c021f1a188a9347e8659ae9a728a09d5b3","tid":2050599,"uid":45270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ced5FGG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCed5FGG.jpg&h=03dc6d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n非打手，有冇人有其他幫助理解同建立政治論述嘅書推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f95bfa34d2addcd34353303b9acd45ad2984bf4","tid":2050599,"uid":45270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433fbbe7d419c7902e82cb8c46c7422fdf3652f6","tid":2050599,"uid":45270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ec61060de3bd8c975ea66714f584ece2e1636c","tid":2050599,"uid":45270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3635961b2ee58e6e40398e90a737d109c20f9d","tid":2050599,"uid":45270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32abddfaf33a94a2a02e7882f0cb75d901963dc1","tid":2050599,"uid":350989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"梁啟智超級左膠喎 寫左本書 &ldquo;獨立路上&rdquo; 本書其實無乜學術內容 吹水書就當學術反港獨 要論述講學術梁啟智真係唔夠班"},{"pid":"907429c5dfac2468fad5a302b8839298218884b9","tid":2050599,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:51:03.000Z","msg":"[思想武裝]我們不妨功利一點看待｢六四｣<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2049910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2049910</a>"},{"pid":"c79d0408fe667693cc692e8870ceccc12eb4214f","tid":2050599,"uid":45270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32abddfaf33a94a2a02e7882f0cb75d901963dc1","tid":20505